            (MonetaryFormat. (.. this negativeSign), (.. this positiveSign), (.. this zeroDigit), (.. this decimalMark), (.. this minDecimals), __decimalGroups, (.. this shift), (.. this roundingMode), (.. this codes), (.. this codeSeparator), (.. this codePrefixed))
