    )

    ;;;
     ; An alias for calling {@link #freshAddress(org.bitcoinj.wallet.KeyChain.KeyPurpose)} with
     ; {@link org.bitcoinj.wallet.KeyChain.KeyPurpose#RECEIVE_FUNDS} as the parameter.
